quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  111,1,"May Abo-Lahab´s both hands waste away and may he waste away [as well]"
  111,2,His wealth and what he´s earned will never profit him
  111,3,he´ll roast in a fire with a flame
  111,4,while his wife who carries kindling around
  111,5,will have a palm-fiber rope around her neck